<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE></DATELINE><TITLE>A Novel Approach for a Novel Pathogen: using a home assessment team to evaluate patients for 2019 novel coronavirus (SARS-CoV-2) | Clinical Infectious Diseases | Oxford Academic</TITLE><BODY>Thousands of people in the United States have required testing for SARS-CoV-2. Evaluation for a special pathogen is resource intensive. We report an innovative approach to home assessment that, in collaboration with public health, enables safe evaluation and specimen collection outside the healthcare setting, avoiding unnecessary exposures and resource utilization.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>